description:
What starts as a routine hockey game quickly spirals into chaos when the violence spills into the stands. As Sam (Mandela Van Peebles) is targeted on the ice, Mike McLusky (Jeremy Renner) is forced to step in showing just how far he’ll go to protect those under his watch. Season 1, Episode 5: Orion
